{"tid":429396,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【真的在市區】黃大仙300呎年輕人恩物 3球有交易","createTime":"2017-10-09T00:35:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-09T00:52:24.000Z","uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"056ab17c1949a95595874f74674c41561c3c6f04","tid":429396,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T00:35:39.000Z","msg":"市區「3字頭」上車盤買少見少，黃大仙蒲崗村道一帶舊樓，仍有400萬元內上車之選，而且實用面積不算勁細，都有逾300方呎，被視為市區窮人恩物。<br />\n<br />\n富誠地產營業董事林栢榮表示，樓價高企，年輕上車客轉購價錢相宜的單幢舊樓。已有近40年樓齡的蒲崗村道慈祥大廈，剛錄得中層H室成交，實用面積313方呎，兩房間隔，座向東南觀街景，剛以325萬元售出，呎價10,383元，買家為年輕上車客。原業主於1988年以26萬元買入單位，持貨29年，賬面獲利299萬元，升值11.5倍。<br />\n<br />\n慈祥大廈由華懋發展，於1978年落成。位置較吊腳，代理指行去地鐵鑽石山站大約15分鐘。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20171008&amp;guid=57306981&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20171008%26guid%3D57306981%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant&d=pJlKXLkXiGzccCl%2Fn%2FAQ6wtTNu1qqkxUxYmVHECffP4%3D&h=92e2eddc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20171008%26guid%3D57306981%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant&h=126d950d\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20171008&amp;guid=57306981&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant</a>"},{"pid":"2ccdf320d12609757b856ddfaef1acd96479e8f8","tid":429396,"uid":10604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T00:43:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8d24514f7e7afa5aa431501de4a70a8375b2112","tid":429396,"uid":81664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T00:45:39.000Z","msg":"40年樓齡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n分分鐘買完仲要俾錢大廈維修"},{"pid":"2cb06003154014e62f53ab94622e2eb0cff30e03","tid":429396,"uid":34773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyT